# Usage:
#    python3 ceph_mds_ops.py [--sort {duration,client,type,uid}] [--min-duration SECS]
#
# ceph_mds_ops - Display Ceph MDS in-flight operations as a formatted table. It queries
# each active MDS rank for ops in flight and resolves client IDs to human-readable
# names using 'ceph tell mds.<rank> dump_ops_in_flight' and 'ceph tell mds.<rank> session ls'.
#
# NOTE: Compatible with python 3.6.8 (Rocky 8)
#

